code: @Override public Object postProcessBeforeInitialization(Object bean, String beanName) throws BeansException {     return bean. }

@Override public Object postProcessAfterInitialization(Object bean, String beanName) throws BeansException {     if (bean instanceof DataSource) {         // force initialization of this bean as soon as we see a DataSource         this.beanFactory.getBean(DataSourceInitializerInvoker.class).     }     return bean. }
